# Day 04 - Modelling a House

## What I Learned
- Modelled a house in Rhino.
- Used ChamferEdge to modify sharp edges.
- Used WireCut to cut geometry.
- Used PushPull to modify solid objects.

## Notes
This lesson was challenging, but I enjoyed learning how the different modelling tools came together to create a house. It was tough, but fun and rewarding.
